						               													<description>From the back of the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Live the final stages of the war and fight on the side of the ninja of the Empire or the mysterious clan able to enslave the spirits of the dead warriors. Team up with your companions against the common enemy but do not hesitate to betray and kill your rivals. Will you be loyal to your clan or to the ninja alliance?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is an expansion pack to the base game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this expansion each eliminated player returns to the game as a spirit in the service of the new NINJA clan, thus forming two factions fighting each other. Each player will never stop playing until the end of the challenge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The expansion also introduces new ways of gaining victory points and a set of psychological challenges among the clans that will determine the final outcome of the war of the shadow of the empire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;---&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vivi le fasi finali  della guerra e combatti dalla parte dei ninja dell'impero o del clan misterioso in grado di assoggettare gli spiriti dei guerrieri eliminati. Alleati con i tuoi compagni contro il nemico comune ma non esitare a tradire ed eliminare i tuoi rivali. Sarai fedele al tuo clan o all'alleanza ninja?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Questa confezione &amp;egrave; un'espansione da abbinare necessariamente al gioco base.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
